description:
The Song of Nunu: Digital Art Book is a bonus for pre-ordering Song of Nunu: A League of Legends Story. Art book includes:

- Early concepts of your favorite characters, both small and yeti-sized
- Environment art from across all corners of the Freljord
- Original artist notes from the creatives behind the game

Art book will be accessible from within the game.
name: Song of Nunu: Digital Art Book
